{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb99c-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7385s–5"},"text":"§ 7385s–5.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Applicability to certain uranium employees","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb99d-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"This part shall apply to—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb99e-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a section 5 payment recipient who contracted a section 5 illness through a section 5 exposure at a section 5 facility, or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb99f-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a section 5 uranium worker determined under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–4/c"},"text":"section 7385s–4(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":" to have contracted a covered illness through exposure to a toxic substance at a section 5 mine or mill,"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"(or to the survivor of that employee, as applicable) on the same basis as it applies to a Department of Energy contractor employee determined under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–4"},"text":"section 7385s–4 of this title","children":[],"tail":" to have contracted a covered illness through exposure to a toxic substance at a Department of Energy facility (or to the survivor of that employee, as applicable)."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb9a0-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Definitions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"In this section:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb9a1-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “section 5 payment recipient” means an individual who receives, or has received, $100,000 under section 5 of the Radiation Exposure Compensation Act (","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2210"},"text":"42 U.S.C. 2210","children":[],"tail":" note) for a claim made under that Act."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb9a2-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The terms “section 5 exposure”, “section 5 facility”, and “section 5 illness” mean the exposure, facility, and illness, respectively, to which an individual’s status as a section 5 payment recipient relates.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb9a3-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “section 5 uranium worker” means an individual to whom subsection (a)(1)(A)(i) of section 5 of the Radiation Exposure Compensation Act applies (whether directly or by reason of subsection (a)(2)).","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb9a4-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa","identifier":"/us/usc/t42/s7385s–5/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The term “section 5 mine or mill” means the mine or mill to which an individual’s status as a section 5 uranium worker relates.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idbe0eb9a5-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/106/398/s1/dC/tXXXVI/s3676"},"text":"Pub. L. 106–398, § 1 [div. C, title XXXVI, § 3676]","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/375/dC/tXXXI/s3161"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–375, div. C, title XXXI, § 3161","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2004-10-28"},"text":"Oct. 28, 2004","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/118/2182"},"text":"118 Stat. 2182","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idbe0eb9a6-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idbe0eb9a7-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idbe0eb9a8-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Radiation Exposure Compensation Act, referred to in subsec. (b), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/101/426"},"text":"Pub. L. 101–426","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1990-10-15"},"text":"Oct. 15, 1990","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/104/920"},"text":"104 Stat. 920","children":[],"tail":", which is set out as a note under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t42/s2210"},"text":"section 2210 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":null}
